Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.73,0:00:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(托朗斯巴皇軍演習場)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.20,0:00:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三...四
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.37,0:00:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿咻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿嘿\N投手漏油！投手漏油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.15,0:00:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好！繼續下去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.55,0:00:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩好球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.25,0:00:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈...還有兩人，還有兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.69,0:00:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意，薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.83,0:00:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡袍...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.46,0:00:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙真是噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.13,0:00:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，每個人的興趣都不同嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.43,0:00:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？那個人穿睡袍嗎？\N嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.97,0:00:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的睡袍...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想了，別想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.88,0:00:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校，宇宙海軍的傢伙\N玩這種比賽真的覺得有趣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.08,0:00:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.68,0:00:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們根本就不想打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且分數已經這麼懸殊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有四個人是第一次打棒球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.89,0:01:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有三個抓來充當球員的機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.63,0:01:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及一個布偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.23,0:01:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種比賽真是沒意義啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因...因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.89,0:01:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.09,0:01:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危機，這下糟糕了\N緊張！緊張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撲克光線  BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.76,0:01:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.83,0:01:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒關係，吃個飲茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.57,0:01:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著歡悅的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.64,0:01:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一起向神明祈禱吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.94,0:01:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.48,0:02:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.15,0:02:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.25,0:02:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它順其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.65,0:02:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有機關，沒有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.23,0:02:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一擲的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無憂無慮的狂歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢想與希望的機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.83,0:02:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖定想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧\NBRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.78,0:02:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人興奮的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.48,0:02:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開闢天下無敵的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(棒球與睡袍白糖)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.20,0:02:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣輸下去的話\N就要陪那個老頭喝酒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.84,0:02:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還要我們穿上\N那件透明的睡袍陪酒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.54,0:03:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，因為一時不小心\N才跟他作了這麼愚蠢的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果天使隊贏宇宙海軍的話\N會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.05,0:03:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅傑中校好像會跳脫衣舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.76,0:03:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果推說那是醉話而不認帳\N不知道行不行得通？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，這倒是個好方法\N就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.90,0:03:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我們有立下誓約書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.94,0:03:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不守約定的話\N我就得辭去軍職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.58,0:03:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！對了，如果輸的話\N天使隊就要改為隸屬於海軍之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.02,0:03:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說我們要成為\N那個老頭的部下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.56,0:03:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.63,0:03:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下個打者怎麼了啊？\N快點！睡袍快點來啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之，我們贏得比賽就行了吧\N贏得比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.84,0:04:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,100比0\N而且我們只剩下一人攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.91,0:04:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要贏！絕對要贏！\N不然我們都要穿透明睡袍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我沒穿過睡袍\N所以要我穿也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.79,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.76,0:04:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那時候\N我們就不是天使隊了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.56,0:04:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是比數100比0\N而且只剩一人攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一定會輸的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我的嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少在那邊囉唆\N想個能贏的方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.68,0:04:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.51,0:04:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是擁有1萬GHzCPU的我\N也沒辦法呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.38,0:04:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.92,0:04:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會贏的\N我有好方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.05,0:04:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要穿泳裝啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不就跟睡袍沒什麼兩樣了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這才是最關鍵的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.93,0:05:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海軍隊的人\N已經迷得無心戀戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有我跟他們說好了\N我們一個人回本壘就能算30分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以只要四人便能逆轉分數了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔，不錯唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過他們說如果讓我們\N我們還是輸的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.78,0:05:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就要請\N佛特和蘭花進行特別服務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時就拜託兩位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼是特別服務？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以請大家一起努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使隊加油\N特別服務是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德，你死也要給我上壘喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是出局的話\N我會把你當作機關鎗的靶子射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.30,0:05:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是失禮\N我的上壘率是百分之百耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.57,0:05:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管她們兩個了\N倒是我...我的香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.84,0:05:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔，真是太美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.44,0:05:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，如果我出局的話\N那麼香草會穿得更清涼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，好想看，好想看\N不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.95,0:06:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，這一棒我要獻給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.46,0:06:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連揮棒都不會\N要怎麼擊球出去啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，這妳就不明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂的打擊，重點不在力氣\N而是時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.96,0:06:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壞球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.00,0:06:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,投手在投球的瞬間\N利用左腳移動體重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩壞球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以球棒的中心擊球...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觸身球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德好厲害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.32,0:06:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個四壞球加一個觸身球\N上壘率的確是百分之百
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好，很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.56,0:06:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要介意\N把下一棒解決，結束比賽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.39,0:06:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼，別想我會出局\N放馬過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.11,0:06:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，我跑不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.67,0:06:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二壘...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全上壘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花好棒，好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是稍微認真了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在看哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，雖然有點擔心\N不過讓下一個出局就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.53,0:07:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也拿出真本領好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.63,0:07:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換投手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.98,0:07:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這邊也要來真的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為贏了就有特別服務可享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，揮棒，揮棒呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.59,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的好運要在這裡使出來呀\N在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，如果出局的話怎麼辦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.94,0:07:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔，如果輸球的話\N天使隊就要消失了
