Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才是妨礙守備啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有意見嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.58,0:09:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來想說妳是小女生\N就算稍微胡鬧也不想跟妳計較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡鬧的人是你吧，還辦這種比賽\N兩位都冷靜一點...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這妳去跟華克說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.69,0:09:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.39,0:09:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛彈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？
