Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.77,0:09:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，NX1855型\N在我兩代前的突擊飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你就叫他爺爺是嗎？
