Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.45,0:09:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它只不過是個未爆彈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.35,0:09:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說，我不是未爆彈\N而是沉睡的獅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.76,0:09:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且甦醒的時候來臨了\N他是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.06,0:10:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什...什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，有件事我忘了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.00,0:10:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的爺爺是搭載了\N專門攻擊指揮官系統的飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.97,0:10:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡單的說就是\N專門瞄準現場最高階的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.87,0:10:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說瞄準你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.41,0:10:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.25,0:10:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華克先生，你和羅傑先生\N一樣都是中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.82,0:10:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你也是會被攻擊的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等...哇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.23,0:10:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶，這樣算是我們贏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比賽也告一段落了\N我們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.77,0:10:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個人不知道能撐到什麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自作自受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.52,0:10:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺，你死得真是壯烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.62,0:10:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差一點就翹辮子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...\NT-MAX5000特別型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.00,0:11:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的青梅竹馬小玉\N原來妳在這裡呀
